Bundled fonts (fonts/)
----------------------
Fortress ships metric-compatible, open-source font faces renamed to the
Windows family names a real Windows browser would expose, so that font-metric
fingerprinting sees a coherent Windows machine. The underlying glyph data is
FOSS:

  * Liberation Sans / Serif / Mono  (-> Arial / Times New Roman / Courier New)
        Copyright Red Hat, Inc.  — SIL Open Font License 1.1 / GPLv2 + Font Exception
  * Carlito                          (-> Calibri)
        Copyright Google / Łukasz Dziedzic — SIL Open Font License 1.1
  * Caladea                          (-> Cambria)
        Copyright Google / Carolina Giovagnoli — SIL Open Font License 1.1
  * Noto Sans / equivalents          (-> Segoe UI, Tahoma, Verdana, Georgia, Consolas)
        Copyright The Noto Project Authors — SIL Open Font License 1.1
  * Noto Color Emoji                 (-> Segoe UI Emoji)
        Copyright The Noto Project Authors — SIL Open Font License 1.1

The fonts have been renamed via their `name` tables. They are NOT the
proprietary Microsoft fonts; only the family-name strings match, for
fingerprint coherence. Each face retains its OFL/GPL license terms. If you
redistribute, retain this NOTICE.
